---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const lang = "en";
---

<Layout
  title="Strategic Advisory | Senquentia"
  description="Strategic advisory services helping organizations navigate complexity and transition."
  lang={lang}
>
  <div class="services-page-wrap">
    <!-- Section 1: Hero -->
    <section class="svc-hero">
      <div class="svc-hero-bg">
        <img src="/images/servicesherobg2.png" alt="" />
      </div>
      <div class="svc-hero-container">
        <div class="svc-hero-box">
          <div class="svc-hero-text-row p-adjust">
            <h1 class="svc-hero-title" style="font-weight: 400;">
              STRATEGIC ADVISORY.
            </h1>
            <div class="svc-hero-bar"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 2: Perspective -->
    <section class="svc-perspective">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="svc-perspective-heading">PERSPECTIVE</h2>

        <div class="svc-perspective-grid">
          <div class="svc-perspective-left">
            <p class="svc-perspective-lead1-strategic">
              Strategic decisions rarely fail because of a lack of ideas.
            </p>
            <p class="svc-perspective-lead2-strategic">
              They fail when organizations struggle to align leadership,
              culture, and execution around a clear direction.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="svc-perspective-divider"></div>
          <div class="svc-perspective-right">
            <p>
              Effective advisory work brings clarity to complex situations,
              helping leadership teams assess their options, evaluate
              organizational readiness, and move forward with confidence.
            </p>
            <p>
              This increasingly includes helping leaders navigate the
              implications of emerging technologies such as artificial
              intelligence on strategy, operating models, and organizational
              readiness.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 3 & 4: Alignment & Impact -->
    <section class="svc-alignment">
      <div class="svc-alignment-bg">
        <img src="/images/servicesherobg2.png" alt="" />
      </div>

      <!-- Alignment Box -->
      <div class="container svc-alignment-container">
        <div class="svc-alignment-box2">
          <div class="svc-alignment-top3">
            <h3 class="svc-alignment-title" style="font-weight: 500;">
              Leadership alignment and strategic clarity shape the decisions
              that define an organization’s direction.
            </h3>
          </div>
          <div class="svc-alignment-bottom-strategic">
            <p class="svc-alignment-desc">
              We work with executive teams to evaluate organizational
              effectiveness, navigate complex decisions, and guide initiatives
              that shape future direction.
            </p>
            <p class="svc-alignment-desc">
              Our role is to provide <strong
                >independent, experience-based perspective</strong
              >, structured analysis and advisory support as leaders navigate
              change, growth, and transformation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 4: Approach -->
    <section class="svc-approach">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="svc-approach-header">
          <h2 class="svc-approach-title">APPROACH</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="svc-approach-list-digital">
          <div class="svc-approach-item">
            <h3 class="svc-approach-item-title">
              Organizational Effectiveness
            </h3>
            <p class="svc-approach-item-text">
              We work with leadership teams to evaluate organizational
              structures, governance models, and decision-making frameworks to
              ensure organizations are positioned to execute their strategic
              priorities effectively.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="svc-approach-item">
            <h3 class="svc-approach-item-title">
              Culture, Leadership & Change Alignment
            </h3>
            <div class="svc-approach-item-text-group">
              <p class="svc-approach-item-text">
                Strategy and transformation succeed when leadership teams are
                aligned around a shared vision, organizational culture supports
                the direction of change, and people are equipped to adapt.
              </p>
              <p class="svc-approach-item-text">
                We support leaders in strengthening alignment, defining cultural
                priorities, and developing leadership capability, while
                embedding practical change management approaches to drive
                adoption and sustain outcomes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="svc-approach-item">
            <h3 class="svc-approach-item-title">Strategic Decision Support</h3>
            <div class="svc-approach-item-text-group">
              <p class="svc-approach-item-text">
                We provide experienced advisory support to leadership teams as
                they navigate complex strategic decisions, helping organizations
                evaluate options, assess risks, and move forward with
                confidence.
              </p>
              <p class="svc-approach-item-text">
                This includes supporting leaders in evaluating the strategic
                implications of technology, transformation investments, and
                emerging capabilities such as artificial intelligence.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="svc-approach-item">
            <h3 class="svc-approach-item-title">
              Transformation & Change Management
            </h3>
            <div class="svc-approach-item-text-group">
              <p class="svc-approach-item-text">
                We help organizations translate strategy into execution by
                designing and guiding structured transformation and change
                initiatives.
              </p>
              <p class="svc-approach-item-text">
                This includes stakeholder alignment, communication strategies,
                adoption planning, and ensuring that changes are effectively
                implemented and sustained across the organization.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 5: Moments -->
    <section class="svc-moments-digital">
      <div class="container svc-moments-container">
        <div class="svc-moments-content">
          <h2 class="svc-moments-title">
            Organizations engage us in moments such as these.
          </h2>
          <div class="svc-moments-line"></div>

          <div class="svc-moments-list">
            <div class="svc-moments-label">Organizational Effectiveness</div>
            <div class="svc-moments-desc">
              Evaluating organizational structures and operating models to
              support strategic priorities
            </div>
            <div class="svc-moments-label">Leadership Alignment</div>
            <div class="svc-moments-desc">
              Assessing leadership alignment and decision-making frameworks
            </div>
            <div class="svc-moments-label">Transformation Readiness</div>
            <div class="svc-moments-desc">
              Preparing for major transformation and change initiatives
            </div>
            <div class="svc-moments-label">M&A and Integration</div>
            <div class="svc-moments-desc">
              Navigating mergers, acquisitions, and strategic integrations
            </div>
            <div class="svc-moments-label">Adoption & Execution</div>
            <div class="svc-moments-desc">
              Driving adoption of new strategies, technologies, and operating
              models
            </div>
            <div class="svc-moments-label">
              Culture & Leadership Development
            </div>
            <div class="svc-moments-desc">
              Strengthening organizational culture and leadership capability
            </div>
            <div class="svc-moments-label">Strategic Transitions</div>
            <div class="svc-moments-desc">
              Supporting leaders through periods of significant change and
              transition
            </div>
            <div class="svc-moments-label">Emerging Technology Strategy</div>
            <div class="svc-moments-desc">
              Evaluating the strategic implications of emerging technologies,
              including artificial intelligence
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 6: Impact -->
    <section class="svc-alignment">
      <div class="svc-alignment-bg">
        <img src="/images/servicesherobg2.png" alt="" />
      </div>

      <!-- Impact Box -->
      <div class="container svc-alignment-container">
        <div class="svc-alignment-box">
          <div class="svc-impact-top">
            <h3 class="svc-impact-title">STRATEGIC CLARITY</h3>
            <div class="svc-impact-text">
              <p>
                Strategic advisory work is ultimately about helping leadership
                teams see their organization more clearly.
              </p>
              <p>
                Our role is to bring independent perspective, structured
                thinking, and practical experience to the decisions that shape
                an organization’s future.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="svc-impact-bottom-strategic">
            <h4 class="svc-impact-footer">
              Navigating critical strategic decisions. Connect.
            </h4>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
